    <item>
      <title>由于利润率担忧，阿斯利康的前景令人失望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/astra-sees-stronger-profit-sales-growth-on-cancer-drugs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿斯利康公司 (AstraZeneca Plc) 公布的利润低于预期，并且今年的预测未能缓解人们对利润率的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/astra-sees-stronger-profit-sales-growth-on-cancer-drugs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 07:15:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着通胀放缓，联合利华希望夺回市场份额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/unilever-returns-to-volume-growth-under-ceo-s-turnaround-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于物价上涨的缓和鼓励购物者购买更多产品，万能冰淇淋制造商联合利华公司两年多以来首次销售了更多产品，如除臭剂和蛋黄酱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/unilever-returns-to-volume-growth-under-ceo-s-turnaround-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 07:10:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国农业信贷银行成本上升令交易结果黯然失色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/credit-agricole-beats-estimates-as-debt-traders-outperform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国农业信贷银行(Credit Agricole SA)在巴黎股市下跌，原因是成本上涨掩盖了该公司和投资银行创纪录的季度业绩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/credit-agricole-beats-estimates-as-debt-traders-outperform</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 06:05:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国第二大金融公司称其拥有 10 亿美元高风险美国房地产赌注，拥有缓冲能力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/korea-s-shinhan-has-buffer-for-1-billion-risky-us-property-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新韩金融集团 (Shinhan Financial Group Co.) 加强了对约 10 亿美元美国高风险房地产风险的缓冲，并表示有信心在冲击全球房地产投资者的信贷担忧浪潮中保持弹性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/korea-s-shinhan-has-buffer-for-1-billion-risky-us-property-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 04:20:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
